description:
THE NEXT EPISODE OF THE ADVENTURES OF PIZARRO AND THE CONQUISTADORS IN THEIR QUEST FOR THE LEGENDARY CITY OF GOLD.

Gold, the wonderful metal will take Francisco Pizzaro on the quest of the Incan empire suffering from a terrible civil war. Armed with barely 180 men and at the head of 3 caravels, Francisco will go looking for the gold of the Cajamarca temple. But beyond the adventure, Illona is who he is looking for, the soul of the plot!
name: Par le feu et par le sang

description:
The Inspector is back! We welcome everyone's favorite klutzy constable back with new adventures and hilarious escapades! And The Pink Panther takes center stage in brand new sidesplitting tales. Get more pink for your green in every issue of The Pink Panther!

description: As ghouls surround her station, KBRF Radio ace DJ Samantha stays on the air all night. Will Rock & Roll save her soul? Burn baby burn. Samantha starts a zombie inferno. Stand back. We don't know how big this girl gets. Sam talks the talk and walks the walk. The End...?
name: Play It Again

description: They're coming to get you Barbara. An old story with a new end and a new beginning. Johnny and Barbara escape from the undead, live through the night, then pick up a hitchhiker on their way home. No good deed goes unpunished. Johnny blacks out, then goes to the kind hospital where patients check in but don't check out. When the rubber hits the road, Johnny and Barbara put the pedal to the metal. The End...?
name: Fall

description:
Desolation

Amidst accusations that he is not Jesus, but rather that he is the Antichrist, Michael questions whether he has interpreted God's plan correctly. He turns to the Bible for answers.
name: Desolation

volume.name: Sennen Sensou Aigis - Eiyuu no Kizuna

description: It’s Rose’s last chance to stop her father before he destroys the shadow glass and the spirit it holds, but a final revelation makes her realize she might be too late.

Even a Brain a-day can't keep this doctor away. Things get weird in the lab when Dr. Grimes feeds a zombie sandwiches, all in the name of science. Bring out your undead... Bring out your undead... I'm not undead yet! Dr. Grimes' experiments aren't brain surgery. Oh, wait, yes they are. The End...?
name: Rigor

description: The posse shoots to kill, but Ben survives. Too bad it's all downhill from here. As the tale unwinds, Chief McClelland and the posse suspect that Ben may not be telling them the whole truth. And they might be right. Good thing Ben has a hard head. If at first you don't succeed, die, die, die again. To avoid the zombie horde, Ben goes back to the drawing board. The End...?
name: Rest In Peace

description: Hot sun, hot babes, and the cold decaying flesh of the zombie horde. She wore an itsy bitsy teeny-weeny yellow polka dot bikini... to the Apocalypse. It's co-eds vs. the undead. The only thing worse than disappearing under the water is being left behind. What goes down must come up. Do these Co-Eds have what it takes? The End...?
name: Torrent

description:
All of the adventures of the Steambusters in one volume! The intrepid trio must do battle with an ageless warrior spirit from ancient China before he destroys the city of London. Set in a unique steampunk world of 1893 England, it is a tale of magic against science, and a tragic love turned to vengeance! This volume also includes the Steambusters' origin story, in which the girls face Jack the Ripper's ghost! Plus "behind the scenes" artwork and creator's notes! Celebrated creator Joe Wight delivers incredible gorgeous artwork and a captivating story! Collects Steambusters #1 and 2.

Note: The digital edition (8/24/2016) for this volume was released before the print edition.
name: TPB

description:
Not so long ago, in a city not so far away...Fred Perry created an amazing new, steampunked take on a space opera classic with Steam Wars. Now, the ace art pilots of Antarctic Press set out to tell their own tales within this universe. Collects Steam Wars: First Empire #1-3.

Note: The digital edition (8/24/2016) for this volume was released before the print edition.
name: Volume One

description: Charlton the Resurrector has arrived! Charlton's a powerful necromancer with a thirst for fame and he's set his sights on Tara's hometown of Little Salem. The Season of Evil has begun.

Supernatural bounty hunter John Tower has long been a man shrouded in mystery. Now, discover what set him on this path of horror as his origins are finally uncovered, revealing just what Tower is risking his life to find!

Now with the vampire Davros' help, Tower and his team travel to Vienna to infiltrate the Brotherhood of the Rose's impregnable castle in search of the last artifact that can free his beloved wife Nadira from purgatory. But new information about the Brotherhood could further endanger their mission...

A breathtaking conclusion in the heart of Troy !

While the last survivors of the Hittite Empire flee the armies of Cronus, Achilles has to enter Troy if he wants to get to the Tartar and free the Giants. But Priam refuses him entry as he considers him an enemy of his people. Against his wishes, Achilles decides to take up arms against the Troy alliance and to fight with King Agamemnon and his brother, the treacherous Menelaus. Achilles knows that he must enter Troy at all costs before Cronus destroys the city and, with it, the last hopes of Humanity…
name: Les Portes du Tartare

description: As Team Voltron searches for a treasure that can settle Coran's debt and save his life, the beasts they have to fight keep getting bigger and nastier! When a mountain monster has Voltron on the ropes, Hunk realizes they'll need more than brute strength to stop it. A never-before-seen chapter of the epic animated series reboot!

Seeing Through New Eyes

Zoe’s powers as the Wellkeeper are revealed to her as Sebastian struggles to regain his memories after he awakens in the body of a raccoon.
name: Seeing Through New Eyes

description: Wonder Woman teams up with a trucker to defeat the Soviet menace! “Worlds Collide” part 2 of 2.
name: Worlds Collide Part 2 of 2

description:
The final question is answered: who will ultimately wield the power of the Wraithborn? The pulse-pounding finale is here as Valin makes a noble attempt to rescue Melanie - and finds himself face-to-face with Brijit and Kiara. The stakes have never been higher, the outcome never more tense. Now is the time when heroes are born - or die.
